sentences: Tisziji Mu√±oz (born July 15, 1946) is an American jazz guitarist.
He left the US Army in 1969.
In the 1970s, he lived in Canada and New York City.
In 1978, he recorded his first album, on the India Navigation label: Rendezvous with Now.
In 1984, he moved to Schenectady.
Along with other musicians, he performed at the 150th anniversary of the Steinway & Sons piano company, at Carnegie Hall, in 2003.
